videos.headline: Perry drops dime to Makekau for the Navy TD

videos.description: Chance Warren takes the reverse and easily gets into the end zone for the 20-yard touchdown.

videos.description: Skylar Thompson gets help from his teammates and powers his way into the end zone for the short touchdown run.
